Interface Tree<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K -

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RedBlackTree

    public interface Tree<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,V>
    The following interface is here to be a template for the red black tree data structure.
    Author:
    Michael Invariant 1: Nodes of the tree contain the color of red or black. Invariant 2: Root node is black. Invariant 3: Leaves have no values and are always black. Invariant 4: If a node is red, then its children are black. Invariant 5: All paths to node leaves should have the same count of black nodes.
